channel.title: And another year passes by for the Axoloti community
channel.description:
Although I cannot say I was there in 2015, I was early 2016, and I just want to say thanks to all for 2017 and the challenges, hopefully not too many left over the next few days, I certainly would not be where I am without the support from you all on my project, I certainly hope you can all say the same and that we can further continue for 2018.:yum:
My current challenge is making 5 expression pedals rather then having to spend $50 each. I can only say one thing.. AAAAHHHHH ! %^&^% :weary: :rofl: All the best to the Axo community.. !:balloon:
